_:N860f302b09f04d9d84b63aeedb2bb8c9 <http://schema.org/description> "We ensure fair payment practices for Britain’s 5.5 million small businesses, and support them in resolving their payment disputes with larger businesses. SBC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Business and Trade ." .
